**Analysis of the Main Target Image**

There are two separate sub‐structures:

1) **Left Tower (7 blocks total, 5 layers):**  
   • **Layer 1 (bottom):** Two cubes side‐by‐side:  
     – Blue on the left  
     – Yellow on the right  
   • **Layer 2:** Two cubes side‐by‐side:  
     – Orange on the left  
     – Red on the right  
   • **Layer 3:** One green rectangular block spanning the full width.  
   • **Layer 4:** One blue cube stacked on the right.  
   • **Layer 5 (top):** One red cube on top of the blue.

2) **Right Arch (6 blocks total, 3 layers):**  
   • **Layer 1 (bottom):** One horizontal yellow rectangular block.  
   • **Layer 2:** A circular “ring” formed by four red arch segments.  
   • **Layer 3 (top):** One horizontal yellow rectangular block matching the bottom.

---

**Block‐Dictionary Matches**  
Using the dictionary image (indices 1–16), the following blocks and orientations match exactly (no rotations allowed):

1) **Left Tower:**
   - Blue cube → index **5** (used twice)  
   - Yellow cube → index **8** (used once)  
   - Orange cube → index **6** (used once)  
   - Red cube → index **7** (used twice)  
   - Green horizontal rectangular → index **9** (used once)

2) **Right Arch:**
   - 4 red arch segments forming a ring → indices **1, 2, 3, 4** (one each)  
   - Yellow horizontal rectangular top & bottom → index **13** (used twice)

---

**Step‐by‐Step Assembly Order**

{  
  Step1:  Move block with index 5   (place bottom‐left blue cube of tower)  
  Step2:  Move block with index 8   (place bottom‐right yellow cube of tower)  
  Step3:  Move block with index 6   (place second‐layer orange cube on left)  
  Step4:  Move block with index 7   (place second‐layer red cube on right)  
  Step5:  Move block with index 9   (place green rectangular block bridging layer 3)  
  Step6:  Move block with index 5   (stack blue cube on layer 4, right side)  
  Step7:  Move block with index 7   (place red cube on top of the tower)  

  Step8:  Move block with index 13  (place bottom horizontal yellow block for arch)  
  Step9:  Move block with index 1   (attach first red arch segment)  
  Step10: Move block with index 2   (attach second red arch segment)  
  Step11: Move block with index 3   (attach third red arch segment)  
  Step12: Move block with index 4   (attach fourth red arch segment to complete ring)  
  Step13: Move block with index 13  (place top horizontal yellow block to finish arch)  
}
